    prompt: 'Schedule and attend mandatory transition job placement assistance at your nearest American Job Center or Veterans Employment Representative office',
    category: 'action',
    helpText: 'American Job Centers and Veterans Employment Representatives provide specialized job search support including resume writing, interview coaching, and direct connections to employers actively hiring veterans in your local area. These federally funded services are specifically designed to help veterans navigate civilian job markets and can provide personalized assistance that general career services cannot match. Attending these sessions connects you with local resources, employer partnerships, and follow-up support throughout your job search process.'
